Platform services and hosting
These services have the purpose of hosting and running key components of Bookbot, therefore allowing the provision of Bookbot from within a unified platform. Such platforms provide a wide range of tools to the Owner  –  e.g. analytics, user registration, commenting, database management, e-commerce, payment processing – that imply the collection and handling of Personal Data.
Some of these services work through geographically distributed servers, making it difficult to determine the actual location where the Personal Data are stored.
Webflow (Webflow, Inc.)
Webflow is a platform provided by Webflow, Inc. that allows the Owner to build, run and host Bookbot. Webflow is highly customizable and can host websites from simple blogs to complex e-commerce platforms.
